items.longDescription: Discover amiibo, a new way to interact with your favorite characters and games. Tap amiibo figures to the Wii U GamePad controller or New Nintendo 3DS XL system to bring them to life in compatible games. Level up amiibo in Super Smash Bros. for Nintendo 3DS and Wii U, get Mii outfits in Mario Kart 8, or play on special game boards in Mario Party 10. Inspired by the Super Mario series, the Super Mario amiibo characters are launching from Nintendo. The lineup includes new models of Mario, Luigi, Peach, Yoshi and Bowser, plus the introduction of the Toad amiibo. amiibo figures that are available in multiple series have the same functionality and compatibility with games, so players can choose which design they like best! Bowser is the king of the Koopas and Mario's eternal rival. He breathes fire, hurls hammers, and uses all sorts of weapons in hopes of taking out Mario. As his size suggests, he's immensely powerful. His plans aren't always the best, and sometimes he even finds himself on Mario's side.<br><br><br><br><br>

items.name: Legend of Zelda Twilight Princess HD with Wolf Link / Midna amiibo (Wii U)
items.categoryPath: Video Games/Nintendo Wii U / Wii/Wii U Games
items.shortDescription: A dark force, shrouded in twilight, has invaded the vast land of Hyrule. To restore light to the world, team up with the mysterious creature Midna and embrace the darkness to transform into a divine wolf. Fight through labyrinthine dungeons, survive puzzling traps, and meet a cast of characters you'll never forget in this legendary Zelda adventure. You can also get an exclusive Wolf Link/Midna amiibo and add bonuses to this title and the upcoming Legend of Zelda game for Wii U, launching in 2016.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess HD is the best way to experience this critically acclaimed game.</li><li>Explore a vast Hyrule, a mysterious Twilight Realm, and masterfully-designed dungeons.</li><li>Restore balance to the world with the aid of the impish Midna and your divine wolf powers.</li><li>Transform into a divine wolf to solve puzzles with your 6th sense and battle creatures corrupted by the twilight.</li><li>Meet a cast of friendly folk and interesting characters, like the entrepreneurial baby Malo and even a yeti couple.</li><li>Nab the exclusive Wolf Link amiibo and carry data over to the upcoming Legend of Zelda game for Wii U, launching in 2016.</li><li>ESRB Rating: TEEN with Animated Blood and Fantasy Violence</li></ul>

items.name: Mega Man Legacy Collection - Collectors Edition - Nintendo 3DS
items.shortDescription: Mega Man Legacy Collection is a celebration of the 8-bit history of Capcom's iconic Blue Bomber. Featuring faithful reproductions of the series' origins with the original six Mega Man games, the Legacy Collection will remind long-time fans and introduce newcomers to what made Mega Man such a popular and iconic character. In addition to the six Mega Man games, Mega Man Legacy Collection features new ways to experience the classic games with the Museum Mode and new Challenge Mode. Challenge Mode remixes gameplay segments from all six games, with plenty of scaling difficulty objectives for experienced players to conquer yet serving as a good starting point for new players, too. Museum Mode contains a comprehensive collection of history, high-res art and original concept pieces - a mega treat for any fan of Mega Man and video game history.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Six classic games in one - Play a piece of video game history with the original six Mega Man games and experience the origins of the classic series.</li><li>8-bit style with HD flair - The games retain their retro 8-bit style with an added HD finish, giving a crisp, clean look to the charming, classic sprites.</li><li>Challenge remix mode for new and veteran players - The robust new Challenge Mode remixes gameplay from all six games for a new type of challenge. It provides both increasingly difficult trials for experienced players and also teaches newcomers to become familiar with the style of the games and tackle some of the trickier areas.</li><li>Museum of the era - The Museum Mode features a massive repository of history and art collected from the era of the games in this collection. Take a look back at the history of Mega Man with loads of information, high-res art, concept pieces, sketches and more in the Museum.</li><li>Developed with an all-new engine - Using the newly developed Eclipse Engine, Capcom and Digital Eclipse are able to archive these six pieces of video game history with faithful reproductions of the originals for a new generation of gamers.</li><li>Leaderboards and video replays - Fans will be able to watch video replays of the top players on the leaderboards, showcasing a whole new generation of Mega Man talent!</li><li>Includes gold Mega Man amiibo.</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with Mild Cartoon Violence</li></ul>

items.name: Animal Crossing: New Leaf (Nintendo 3DS) - Pre-Owned
items.shortDescription: Animal Crossing: New Leaf is loaded with new characters, items, and activities to enjoy all year long. Customize outfits in countless ways. Furnish your house with an extensive variety of furniture, carpet, and wall decorations to reflect your personality. Visit the new Main Street shopping area and Happy Home Showcase. Swim in the ocean to find rare shellfish. Collect insects and fossils all year long. As mayor, make the big decisions about what to build, business hours for shops, and other new ways to customize your town to your liking. Then connect with friends to show off what makes your character, your house, and your town unique. Use Parental Controls to restrict 3D mode for children 6 and under.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Welcome to Animal Crossing: New Leaf - Create your very own happy place in the wonderful world of Animal Crossing. Come in and look around - and see why there's no other place quite like it.</li><li>It's Not Just a Game... It's a Way of Life - There are no points or levels, just an amazing array of sights and sounds, places and activities... all yours to explore. Spend your time passing new ordinances - or going fishing. Hang out at a coffee shop or visit a tropical island. It's all up to you.</li><li>Totally Unique... Just Like You - Your game is what you make it - and personalizing your world is part of the fun. Create cool patterns for clothing or furniture, build new structures in your own, design gardens and museum displays, and so much more.</li><li>New Day, New Discoveries - Time passes in the world of Animal Crossing just as it does in real life. Celebrate holidays and see the seasons change. Meet new visitors or get gifts from your neighbors. There's always something special to look forward to.</li><li>A Natural World - The great outdoors can play as big a part in Animal Crossing as you want it to. Spend time planting trees, picking fruit, digging for fossils, and arranging flowers. Grab a net and fishing rod to collect all kinds of insects and fish. Or just sit back and enjoy the scenery.</li><li>New Friends - As you build your town, new animals will move in and say "hello." There are dozens of charming characters in the game to get to know. You can even visit the towns of other players (either online or locally) and invite the characters you meet along the way to move to your town.</li><li>Lots of Shopping - One of the many fun things to do in Animal Crossing is finding ways to spend your Bells (the local currency). Collect furniture for your dream home, buy new clothes, or shop at the flea market. With hundreds of items to buy, sell, or trade, there's always shopping to do.</li><li>ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with Comic Mischief</li></ul>

items.name: Fire Emblem Fates: Birthright (Nintendo 3DS)
items.shortDescription: Your battle. Your future. Your fate. Two kingdoms are on the brink of war. Whose side will you choose? Torn between two families, you're an heir of Hoshido, raised by Nohrian royals. If you choose the path of Birthright, you'll battle the corrupted king of Nohr beside a family of strangers. If you walk the path of Conquest, you must fight to change your misguided kingdom from within. Command warriors with expert precision and forge deep relationships to master this turn-based strategy game.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Each path is a complete story and a complete game. Playing both will show you two different sides of one brutal conflict.</li><li>For the first time in the Fire Emblem series, your customized avatar is the main character.</li><li>Epic storyline centered on your avatar, forced to choose between bloodline and family who raised you.</li><li>New "My Castle" area allows you to interact with your allies and build stronger relationships.</li><li>Tap in corresponding compatible Fire Emblem amiibo figures and Marth, Ike, Lucina, and Robin will appear in your game, ready for you to battle and recruit.</li><li>A third story path will be available for owners of Fire Emblem Fates: Birthright or Fire Emblem Fates: Conquest to buy digitally in-game, called Fire Emblem Fates: Revelation.</li><li>Downloadable content (DLC) will be available, including one free map and six additional maps for purchase.</li><li>ESRB Rating: TEEN with Animated Blood, Suggestive Themes, and Fantasy Violence</li></ul>

items.shortDescription: Control the skies in beautifully enhanced 3D on the New Nintendo 3DS XL System!
